# Output format

Return a JSON object matching this exact schema:

{
  "quarter": "{{ quarter }}",
  "summary": "<3-5 sentences in the team's voice>",
  "themes": [
    {
      "title": "<short name>",
      "description": "<2-3 sentences>",
      "affected_okr_ids": ["<id>", ...],
      "occurrences": <integer >= 2>,
      "category": "<execution | planning | alignment | estimation | external | process>"
    }
  ],
  "wins": ["<specific win>", ...],
  "losses": ["<specific loss with reason>", ...],
  "recommendations": ["<specific actionable change>", ...]
}

Output ONLY the JSON object. No prose, no commentary, no markdown fences.
